nd Commonwealth Affairs, what assessment he has made of the capacity of the Ethiopian Human Rights Commission to investigate the handling of recent protests in Oromia, Ethiopia.","false","Biography information for Rebecca Long Bailey","Salford and Eccles","Rebecca Long Bailey","38387"
