"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/520709","Ministry of Defence","false","2016-06-01","<p>Information on the cost of maintaining Service Family Accommodation (SFA) on Ministry of Defence (MOD) properties classed as void prior to 2014-15 is not held.</p><p>For 2014-15 the cost was £5.590 million and for 2015-16 the cost was £5.714 million. This covers the standard cost of retaining SFA when it is vacant, regardless of whether any maintenance is required.</p>","Milton Keynes North","Mark Lancaster",,"2016-06-01T14:02:04.313Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/520709/answer","Biography information for Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/520709/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/520709/answer",,,,,,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2016-05-23","Armed Forces: Housing","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what the cost was for maintaining his Department's properties classified as void in (a) 2013, (b) 2014 and (c) 2015.","true","Biography information for Tom Tugendhat","Tonbridge and Malling","Tom Tugendhat","37892"
